Text: Re RE Bachelor party Cc Hey fellas Im not going to make it this weekend Too many obligations here in WF and too far to go Wish I could be there Yall will have a blast Give Dave my best Email me at work I check that one more often Take care God Bless Tommy Original Message From Taylor Michael E Sent Wednesday October AM To Cc Subject RE RE Bachelor party I think Paintball looks good I think we should just all go to the store together and split the cost of the alcohol Also maybe play some poker at the house at night Maybe everybody can bring a few dollars for a house game No preference on the cake Oh Tommy are you coming to the party Luke please give my address to Bridgett S Heights Blvd Apt Houston tx LATER Mike From Brian Craig To Beau M Romero Mike Taylor Email Richard L Millette Email Subject RE Bachelor party Date Tue Oct Hey guys Hows this look I emailed them for pricing information and Ill let you know what they come back with Also how do you guys want to do the alcohol Everyone bring something Go out and get it that day Other suggestions Since were not having live girls I was considering about having a busty cake made Good idea Bad idea Any other ideas Cheers Brian
